Text:
The overall champion of this year's Great Ize-athlon
is Alpha!

It was full of crazy contests. I guess those are
therianthropes for you...

Now we can get kagami rice cake! And give it to
Boss man!

We will now present the winner with kagami rice cake!
But before that...!

It did feel like they were holding something back
before the announcement... What now?
We will have an exhibition match of "Death Ending"!
Yeah! We've been waiting!

What on earth is a Death Ending... That sounds rather
alarming.
It's fine. There is nothing to be scared of.

This year's top two contestants! Delta, Alpha, this
way please!

You two will enter the cage with the beast, Shishi,
and give him the right to eat death!
Shishi? Delta, do you know about this?
Yeah. He's a big beast, but people-friendly.
(If Delta says so, then it should be okay.)

Playing with Shishi and letting him lick you will let
him eat the bad air and aura of death that surrounds
people.

It is the end of deathâ€•Death Ending is an honor we
give to the top two contestants.

Very well...if it's part of the ceremony then we had
better finish it, or we will never get the kagami rice
cake.

Please, this way! Please go inside! We only just
caught him, but he is a messenger of the gods!

He's so big. I'll bet he breaks his opponent even if
he's just playing.
Thank you for clarifying that this is how he "plays."

Well, we could ask him to bite whatever part he likes,
legs or arms or head, and get this done with.
Huh? But take a good look at him...
What? Is there something else?
Grrr...
I knew it...! This isn't Shishi, it's Shishiodoshi.
It's a different animal? What will Shishiodoshi do?

He was just pretending to be Shishi to get close!
He'll swallow ya whole if you aren't ready!

They didn't see through Shishiodoshi's acting and
caught him thinking he is Shishi... Oh dear.
Grrr...

What is Shishiodoshi? He's not calm and tender and
likely to give up on us...?
More like he's hungry and wants a snack.
I thought so... We can't escape.

What should we do? Hunt him? Or stalk him and then
hunt him?

We can't do that. There are so many tourists at this
New Year festival.

If we make a big uproar, everyone will get thrown
into chaos, and we might cause an even bigger
disaster.

Also, if this event gets suspended, we won't be able
to get that kagami rice cake we've earned.

Ha-ruff... That'd mean we lose everything we worked so
hard for!
So to prevent that, let's deal with this quietly.
Grrrr... Slurrrrp.

We have to make it seem like he is licking our faces
and being playful, and then carefully hit him without
bringing attention to ourselves.

If we can stun him and make it look like he fell
asleep, to others it will look like he got tired and
dozed off.
...I see! Lady Alpha, you're sure amazing!
Grrr... Grraaaaahh!
This year's Shishi is really active!

But this year's winners are super strong too.
I'm getting all excited!

For better or worse, no one has noticed it is
Shishiodoshi. If possible, we need to end this
without them noticing...
All right, Delta. Slowly and quietly, okay?

Got it! Same as Boss man. Delta will be strong like
Boss man!
I'm not sure if you really understand...
Brrr... Grraaaaahh!

We need to take care of him before he eats us!
Discretely, like we're going to pet him...
Gaaahh!
He's got a hold of my head!
*chomp, chomp*
Ah, he's chewing on her! He's play-biting!
Play biting? These fangs hurt...!

Delta, even if it hurts, be patient. Now to make it
look like I'm going to pet him...
Graar, grarrr...!
Hahaha, he's opening his mouth!

The damage reached his internal organs. His mouth is
open wide because he's struggling to breathe.
Graaa!!
Ow! If he'd bitten down, it would've cut my throat.

Okay, now... We pretend to dance to get closer to
Shishiodoshi, and make it look like we are petting
him, then drive a blow into his belly!
Yeah! We'll teach you who is stronger!
